Program 2: Find Square or Cube

Criteria:

If number is 0 or Negative â†’ return -1
If number is even â†’ return square
If number is odd â†’ return cube

SquareAndCube.java
package com.ravi.blc;

public class SquareAndCube {
    public static int findSquareAndCube(int num) {
        if (num <= 0) {
            return -1;
        } else if (num % 2 == 0) {
            return num * num;
        } else {
            return num * num * num;
        }
    }
}

